adithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20836,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/08\/17\/father-middle-door-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37828,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Parents: Father is middle gate of Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 17, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe father is the middle of the gates of Paradise. If you wish, you can squander this gate or keep to it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1900 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u064e\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42135,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/08\/22\/tawheed-reaches-arsh\/","url_meta":{"origin":37828,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: It reaches the Throne if major sins avoided","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 22, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNever does a servant sincerely say, \u2018There is no God but Allah,\u2019 but that the gates of heaven open for it, even leading to the Throne itself, as long as he avoids major sins.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646